(52, '高校女生节活动花样百出，“三七”vs“三八”争议不断', '女生节活动花样百出', '<p><span style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87);">女生节的渊源</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp; 1986年3月7日，山东大学文学与新闻传播学院、经济学院女生节联欢晚会在山东大学东校区科学会堂举行。&ldquo;追溯女生节的来源，是由于高校女生不愿意称自己为妇女，但是又不想放弃女性节日的特权。&rdquo;此后&ldquo;各大媒体分别就&lsquo;女生节&rsquo;这一&lsquo;新生事物&rsquo;做了详尽的跟踪报道，女生节逐渐在象牙塔间蔓延。随着社交网络的发达，各地大学零散的庆祝在虚拟空间遥相呼应，影响溢出校园，最终汇聚成一个青年女子的民间节日。&rdquo;其中不乏全国性的轰动话题，譬如2012年清华北大女生节横幅PK事件。</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87);">女生节&ldquo;城会玩&rdquo;</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp; &nbsp;3月6日，浙江各大高校掀起了各式各样的女生节活动。其中，浙江大学各学园打出风格迥异的电子屏祝福；浙江工商大学校园内拉起了诸如&ldquo;我是9，你是3，我除了你还是你&rdquo;、&ldquo;校外饿狼成群，校内美女如云&rdquo;等幽默横幅；浙江传媒学院女生节当天，在体育馆对面展出了一个插满玫瑰的大喷绘&hellip;&hellip;</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><a href="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/E98H7dujLV4kEBmwtR9h1OmzpusjAwgEzic07Lic9s8TazfbdVUS5Rpibc25a9PaVPve32yTE8UJcaraibnChJxbNA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1"></a></span><img class="fr-dib" src="http://www.campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/56deae0ea5435.jpeg" style="width: 470px;"></p><p><img class="fr-dib" src="http://www.campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/56deae3c32d81.jpeg" style="width: 468px;"><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 19px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 浙传玫瑰喷绘</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 19px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img class="fr-dib" src="http://www.campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/56deaeca30bb9.jpeg" style="width: 469px;"></span><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 19px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;浙大电子屏祝福</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 19px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img class="fr-dib" src="http://www.campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/56deaf32dffe2.jpeg" style="width: 474px;"></span><img class="fr-dib" src="http://www.campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/56deaf4a78d5e.jpeg" style="width: 473px;"><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 19px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 清华女生节横幅</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif;">&nbsp; 除了往年常见的女生节横幅集锦，今年全国各高校的女生节活动花样百出，网友纷纷评论&ldquo;城会玩&rdquo;。</span></p><p></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp; 你还记得《怦然心动》里的&ldquo;篮子男孩&rdquo;吗？3月6日，为庆祝女生节，广州华南师范大学石牌校区真的举办了一场 &ldquo;竞拍男生&rdquo;活动。8名风格各异的男生施展浑身解数，表演各自才艺，以求女生出高价&ldquo;买&rdquo;走。一旦竞拍成功，被竞拍走的男生需全天为获得者服务，满足她的合理要求。</section><p></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img class="fr-dib" src="http://www.campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/56deafc14200c.jpeg" style="width: 463px;"></section><br><p></p><p><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">烟台大学人文学院中141-3团支部的同学们就过了一个别开生面的女生节。班里的男生纷纷化妆庆祝女生节，度过特殊的一天。</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img class="fr-dib" src="http://www.campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/56deaff88995d.jpeg" style="width: 463px;"></span><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">3月7日，天津南开大学举办第三届&ldquo;女大学生就业创业&rdquo;专场校园双选会，房地产、医药、教育等产业的60余家企业参会，提供岗位约520个，为即将毕业的女大学生带来专属关怀。双选会现场还开辟美容专区，专业化妆师免费为女大</span><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">学生化妆。</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp; <img class="fr-dib" src="http://www.campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/56deb19bc3e41.jpeg" style="width: 459px;"></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87);">争议：</span><span style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87);">&ldquo;女生节 or 妇女节&rdquo;</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp; 不同于以往的是，今年的女生节，超出了原本的娱乐性质，&ldquo;三七&rdquo;与&ldquo;三八&rdquo;的争议带来了更多关于女性权利的思考。</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">不久前，《奇葩说》一辩手范湉湉在微博上发起了＃女生节取代妇女节＃的话题，瞬间一呼百应。有人赞同就有人指责，微博＃反三七过三八＃话题同样声势浩大，李思磐罗列女生节三宗罪：分裂&ldquo;妇女&rdquo;、&ldquo;女生&rdquo;阵营；把妇女节的&ldquo;权利&rdquo;主题偷换成&ldquo;关系&rdquo;，成为男性的异性恋式示好表演；让意淫和消费假关爱之名成为传统与惯例。</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img class="fr-dib" src="http://www.campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/56deb0b234172.jpeg" style="width: 335px;"></span><br></p><p><img class="fr-dib fr-img-move" src="http://www.campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/56deb0c875ee2.jpeg" style="width: 329px;"></p><p></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp; 或许事实上，两者都走向了极端。女生节与妇女节本就是面向不同对象的节日，妇女通常指的更多的是已婚女性，女生节的出现更多的只不过是为了满足非婚女孩的想要度过关于女性的节日的需求罢了。女生节确实无法取代妇女节对于争取女性权利的历史意义，也不应该去取代。但将女生节完全视为男权视角下的产物，是否走得有些过远了？照这么说，我们又该如何看待男生节呢？</section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp; &nbsp;妇女节目前的尴尬地位不应简单归咎于女生节的盛行，对于女性权利的争取也不是通过简简单单的&ldquo;反三七&rdquo;可以做到的。性别歧视的广泛存在也不是一年中某一天的口号式的呼喊可以抹去的。在消费主义盛行的今天，我们更应该冷静理性地思考，拿出更多的实际行动与解决方案。</section><p></p>', '2016-03-08 19:05:58', 71, '8', 3, 33, 0, '56deb21643688.jpeg', '56deb21643688_thumb.jpeg'),
(54, '斩获了奥斯卡的小李子，投资竟然也这么牛！', '颇具商业头脑的“小李子”在斩获奥斯卡之前，早在投资界就拿到了“小金人”。', '<p class="text" style="margin: 25px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: arial, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">北京时间2.29中午，第88届奥斯卡颁奖典礼在美国洛杉矶的杜比剧院举行。在&ldquo;专业陪跑20年&rdquo;之后，凭借《荒野猎人》，莱昂纳多&middot;迪卡普里奥终于问鼎奥斯卡，夺得最佳男主角奖。其实，颇具商业头脑的&ldquo;小李子&rdquo;在斩获奥斯卡之前，早在投资界就拿到了&ldquo;小金人&rdquo;。</span></p><p class="text" style="margin: 25px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: arial, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">莱昂纳多14岁出道，凭借《泰坦尼克号》一举成名，如今，身处演艺圈将近30年的他累计财富已经超过百亿。有人说他，明明可以靠脸吃饭，他偏偏把脸(和身材)毁了，一次又一次地证明，自己靠才华也没问题。</span></p><h2 style="margin: 25px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; font-family: arial, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">投资社交网站Mobli</span></h2><p class="text" style="margin: 25px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: arial, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">2011年，莱昂纳多用四百万美金成为社交网站Mobli的投资人。这家2010年成立的社交网站类似Instagram、Viddy和Socialcam，主要是关于用户照片和视讯的分享。</span></p><p class="text" style="margin: 25px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: arial, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">据报道，自从Mobli于2009年诞生以来，2012年就达到了200万用户，2013年底已经达到1200万用户。现在也可以实现直播、音乐、文字、位置的分享，更加丰富了使用场景，可以使用户了解到所在方位正在发生的故事，也能为用户提供身边的餐馆、超市等功能搜索。2015年又推出了实时图片搜索引擎 EyeIn，到目前为止已融资约 8600 万美元。而作为明星投资人的&ldquo;小李子&rdquo;还一度成为网站的颜值担当。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px;"><img class="fr-dib" src="http://www.campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/56df921c1263c.jpg" style="width: 600px;"></span><br></p><div><h2 style="margin: 25px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; font-family: arial, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">投资钻石公司Diamond Foundry</span></h2><p class="text" style="margin: 25px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: arial, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">在电影《血钻》里，莱昂纳多饰演了一个彻头彻尾的战争贩子，以倒卖钻石和军火为生，在目睹了钻石带来的种种残酷与腐败后，幡然悔悟。而在戏外，他的确投资了一家做钻石的创业公司。2015年11月，莱昂纳多在其个人推特发布其参与投资Diamond Foundry，这将一定程度缓解人类和环境因为开采钻石而带来的损害。该公司创始人宣称，他们能够在两周之内制造出和天然钻石一样的钻石来，这些钻石最大能够达到 9 克拉。</span></p><h2 style="margin: 25px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; font-family: arial, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 14px;"><img class="fr-dib" src="http://www.campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/56df9229a2ca2.jpg" style="width: 334px;"><br></h2><h2 style="margin: 25px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; font-family: arial, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">投资垃圾运输界的Uber</span></h2><p class="text" style="margin: 25px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: arial, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">2015年9月 ，莱昂纳多投资了一家创业公司垃圾运输界的Uber&mdash;&mdash;Rubicon Global。据报道，这家公司从类似711这样的商业用户那里收取垃圾，然后找到离他们最近的垃圾处理站进行回收处理，Rubicon 被人称作&ldquo;垃圾处理界的Uber&rdquo;，代表了废旧产品处理行业的改革潮流。据悉，这家公司还雇佣了Uber的前CFO布伦特&middot;卡里尼克斯。</span></p><h2 style="margin: 25px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; font-family: arial, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 14px;"><img class="fr-dib" src="http://www.campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/56df9239371b7.jpg" style="width: 458px;"><br></h2><h2 style="margin: 25px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; font-family: arial, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">投资车队参加Formula E</span></h2><p class="text" style="margin: 25px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: arial, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">2012年7月，莱昂纳多成为美国环保汽车制造商菲斯克汽车公司的新任股权投资者。他借着自己在好莱坞的人气，不遗余力地配合菲斯克公司在新车型等项目上面的宣传。尽管菲斯克不久之后就宣布停产，但莱昂纳多对电动车的坚持一如既往。</span></p><p class="text" style="margin: 25px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: arial, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">2013年12月，&ldquo;小李子&rdquo;和Venturi汽车合资组建了一支车队参加2014年开赛的Formula E，而且车队拿到了第十个也是最后一个参加2014/15赛季电动方程式的名额。Venturi汽车集团曾经生产过号称&ldquo;全球速度最快&rdquo;的电动汽车Venturi VBB3。</span></p><h2 style="margin: 25px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; font-family: arial, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 14px;"><img class="fr-dib" src="http://www.campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/56df925945a61.jpg" style="width: 496px;"><br></h2><h2 style="margin: 25px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; font-family: arial, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">投资在线床垫零售商Casper</span></h2><p class="text" style="margin: 25px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: arial, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">在线床垫零售商Casper，是一家估值为5亿5千5百万的企业，成立仅28天就赚取了100万美元的收入。这家做床垫生意的创企有大批阵容的明星投资者。据报道，公司已经从InstitutionalVenture Partners （IVP）领导的投资中筹集了5500万美元，参投方除了全美最富裕的普利兹克家族外，还包括莱昂纳多。</span></p><h2 style="margin: 25px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; font-family: arial, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 14px;"><img class="fr-dib" src="http://www.campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/56df926545f53.jpg" style="width: 485px;"><br></h2><h2 style="margin: 25px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; font-family: arial, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">投资房产，11年间赚了1135万美元</span></h2><h2 style="margin: 25px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; font-family: arial, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 14px;"><p class="text" style="margin: 25px 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><span style="font-size: 18px;">据外媒报道称，&ldquo;小李子&rdquo;在美国甚至全球都拥有房产。他在2002年以600万美元在加州马里布买下临海大屋，2013年10月底以1735万美元成功出售，11年间赚了1135万美元。而且SOHO中国CEO张欣的那套2600万美元豪宅，就是从他手下抢过来的。</span></p><p class="text" style="margin: 25px 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><span style="font-size: 18px;">本文内容转载自姑婆那些事儿（</span><span style="font-size: 18px;"><a href="http://gupowang.baijia.baidu.com/article/336561">www.gupowang.com</a></span><span style="font-size: 18px;">)</span></p></h2></div>', '2016-03-09 11:04:42', 93, '8', 8, 36, 0, '56df92ca3f393.jpg', '56df92ca3f393_thumb.jpg'),
(69, '不想睡宋仲基的大学生不是好大学生', '现在的大学生是“怎么了”？', '<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">我发现中国的新闻有个规律，只要一沾上&ldquo;大学生&rdquo;三个字就能火。如果再加上具体的校名就更好了，比如杀人案，放在新闻里，大概只能呆在边角，可是要是&ldquo;北大学生弑母&rdquo;，那是可以上头条的，当然最好是女大学生。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">这样的标题实在是太适合引起网络狂欢了。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">同样的还有这个新闻，武汉大学辩论队奇葩队名引讨论，武汉大学的学生不过起了这么几个名字。</p><p><img class="fr-dib" src="http://www.campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/56f12e6331eb0.jpeg" style="width: 398px;"></p><p><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">通篇看下来我觉得没有什么可以吐槽的地方，除了笑傲江湖和倚天屠龙这种名字太缺乏创意以外，可有人并不这么想。</span></p><p><img class="fr-dib" src="http://www.campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/56f12ef412eb2.jpeg" style="width: 345px;"></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">我能隔着屏幕感受到评论者的痛心疾首，甚至我能想象他捶胸顿足想要喊出那句&ldquo;中国的大学生怎么了？&rdquo;再加上一句，&ldquo;救救教育，救救孩子&rdquo;几乎就完美了。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">中国的大学生怎么了你不应该问大学生啊。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">你应该看看这个新闻，<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);">浙江省教育厅和人大代表来大学检查宿舍卫生</span></strong>。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">从3月7日开始，由浙江省教育厅及相关组织组成的督查组，每月将对全省高校学生寝室卫生环境情况随机进行大检查，检查不合格寝室情况将通报给学校，并对全省高校进行排名。更有甚者，&ldquo;宿舍卫生还要跟期末成绩挂钩&rdquo;。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">这个新闻好，好在一下子点出了两个群体的尴尬，一个是人大代表，一个是高校。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">一纸行政命令，就能随意更改游戏规则，干预学校的管理。高校的尴尬地位连人大代表都不如，不过是匍匐在权力脚下的奴隶。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">评论者从哪里来的错觉中国的大学是&ldquo;象牙之塔&rdquo;，中国的大学生是&ldquo;天之骄子&rdquo;。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">实际上，根本不想要他们成为天之骄子。他们真正想要的大学生应该是这个样子。</p><p><img class="fr-dib" src="http://www.campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/56f13229105e0.jpeg" style="width: 469px;"></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">这才是理想的大学生嘛，小了说不给大学添麻烦，大了说不给国家添麻烦，这么小就会说官面文章，这才是国家的栋梁之才。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">我觉得大学生真的都变成这样？才应该有人站出来问一句，中国的大学生怎么了？高校早都行政化，学术早都政治化，也没见有人站出来问？</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">所以不要说大学生不忧国忧民，不优雅，不高大上，大学生在这样的社会里不忧国忧民怎么了？真的忧国忧民破坏了安定团结怎么办？</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 25.6px;">中国大学生的尴尬地位，他们早已失去了精英的地位，但在形象和道德上，社会和权力却要求他们保持精英式的价值观。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 25.6px;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 25.6px;">这种尴尬，不止是大学生，整个学术界都不能幸免。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">这样的尴尬地位还能要求大学生们怎么样？看看剧，玩玩流行词挺好，还参加辩论赛，还好好学习，挺充实的。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.6;">其实身在所谓&rdquo;象牙塔&ldquo;之中的人，早都放下了，我们哪有什么武汉大学，我们不是只有珞珈山综合职业培训学校吗？我们哪有北大，我们不是只有中关村应用文理学院吗？我们哪有清华，我们明明只有五道口职业技术学校，哦，男子。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.6;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.6;">这样的自嘲说明早都不以精英自命，社会也大可不必把每次把使命感和责任感拿出来说事，怪吓人的，大家一起快活地刷剧不好吗？</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.6;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.6;">想睡宋仲基怎么了？我还想睡宋慧乔呢,从小时候就想。</span></p><p><img class="fr-dib" src="http://www.campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/56f132b11ef73.jpeg" style="width: 450px;"></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 25.6px;">至少想睡宋仲基不犯法，说明在国家和人民这样的关注之下，中国的女大学生和部分男大学生的三观和审美都没有扭曲，哪天想睡我了才是不正常呢。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 25.6px;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 25.6px;">大学生们还是好得很，只是社会有点不太好而已。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 25.6px;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 25.6px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 25.6px;">这样的环境里，学生变成精致的利己主义者也好，变成消费主义者也好，甚至变成官僚主义者，都不过是阉割高校和学术界的自然结果，求仁得仁，又有何怨？</span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.6;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.6;">实在太有责任感和使命感的，也不要总是问&ldquo;中国的大学生怎么了？&rdquo;&ldquo;中国的教育怎么了？&rdquo;不要总想着救救教育，救救孩子，宝宝们好得很，先救救那啥。</span></p><p><strong>原文作者：</strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center; white-space: pre-wrap; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">霍真布鲁兹老爷</strong></p><p><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center; white-space: pre-wrap; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span>转载自微信公众号：霍老爷的小木屋</strong></p>', '2016-03-22 19:59:25', 82, '8', 8, 29, 0, '56f1339d00d3f.jpg', '56f1339d00d3f_thumb.jpg');
