(82, '【卫生检查】快给女生寝室来包去污粉！', '女生寝室的终极秘密！！', '<p style="text-align: center;"><br></p><div style="text-align: center;"><section><section><section><section><p style="text-align: center;"><span>萌妹纸？</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span>软妹纸？</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span>女神？</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span>女汉纸？</span></p></section></section></section></section><section><section><section><p style="text-align: center;"><span>每朵白莲花背后都有你意想不到的</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span>污泥~~~~</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span>你以为兔子都不沾荤腥~洁白如雪！</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span>其实偶们只是躲在寝室里默默</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span>吃！烧！烤！</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span>今天！让我们一起来八一八</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span>女生寝室那些不得不说的段子</span><span>吧！</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span><strong><span><br></span></strong></span><br></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span><strong><span>闺中秘语&nbsp;</span></strong></span></p><p>OR</p></section></section></section><section><section><section><section><strong><span>污山夜话</span></strong></section><p style="text-align: center;"><br></p></section><img src="https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/rgl3xY3CiaFb6H0DR5eOH9ufhv8vwTwicI1eX3hicyxgrhicH9Dqib1o9JJPjWFvP66svt9TmMLpW5dRh5D1y9GvISA/0?wx_fmt=png" data-ratio="0.09712230215827339" data-w="" class="fr-dii" style=""><span>&nbsp;</span></section></section><section><section><section><section><strong>1</strong></section></section></section></section><section><section><section><section><br></section><section>我们寝室的床是上下铺，</section><section>上铺每天都会对下铺说，</section><p style="text-align: center;">呀！你又睡在我下面！</p><p style="text-align: center;"><br></p><section><img data-s="300,640" data-type="png" src="https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/E98H7dujLV5ozib26aXThep73b8EcYGNiaTxUO6HJtFI9XrM6DI3vaIW77ibd7xnOMKicoCDdzehur8sWI5P3oOLzA/0?wx_fmt=png" data-ratio="0.9174757281553398" data-w="206" class="fr-dii" style=""></section></section></section></section></div><div style="text-align: center;"><section><section><section><section><br></section></section></section></section><section><section><section><section><strong>2</strong></section></section></section></section><section><section><section><section><br></section><section>&lsquo;&rsquo;你晚上还回来不？&lsquo;&rsquo;</section><section>&ldquo;当然回来啊！&rdquo;</section><section>&ldquo;你就浪外边吧！回来干嘛啊～&rdquo;</section><section>&ldquo;我回来干你啊！&rdquo;</section><p style="text-align: center;">&ldquo;&hellip;&hellip;&rdquo;</p><p style="text-align: center;"><br></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="png" src="https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/E98H7dujLV5ozib26aXThep73b8EcYGNiasgQTdVmHgjgL4ic7dGlvgHcsSwIykLehETt0Wbn7S3eicwNUaFuKKlgQ/0?wx_fmt=png" data-ratio="0.5678571428571428" data-w="280" class="fr-dii" style=""><br></p></section></section></section><section><section><section><section><br></section></section></section></section><section><section><section><section><strong>3</strong></section></section></section></section><section><section><section><section><br></section><section>过年那天，我收到一条这样的拜年短信：</section><section>我想把你甩在床上，</section><section>看着你不安的双眼，</section><section>撕开你的衣服，</section><section>低头吻上你的锁骨，</section><section>轻咬一口，听着你轻喘一声，</section><section>然后双腿勾上我的腰，在你耳边吐气，</section><section>&nbsp;听你向我求饶，然后把你壁咚，</section><section>看你脸红的样子，慢慢的侵蚀你的嘴唇，</section><section>双手慢慢深入你的衣衫，抚摸你的肌肤，</section><p style="text-align: center;">在你耳根说:给你拜年了！</p><p style="text-align: center;"><br></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" src="https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/E98H7dujLV5ozib26aXThep73b8EcYGNiaOtHdcmSkaKLNjdrsB7gmpIlqopu7MwXtoAz1ZEJskqjyTcnADQAGRA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="1.065909090909091" data-w="440" class="fr-dii" style=""><br></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br></p></section></section></section><section><section><section><section><br></section></section></section></section><section><section><section><section><strong>4</strong></section></section></section></section><section><section><section><section><br></section><section>室友：你觉得我优点是什么？</section><p style="text-align: center;">我：胸一甩奶四海</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="png" src="https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/E98H7dujLV5ozib26aXThep73b8EcYGNiaButGlme47stvUB3F1NIH5rsCl67Y55dARoCiclmVvSoDSlSBKgFY9HA/0?wx_fmt=png" data-ratio="0.3452914798206278" data-w="446" class="fr-dii" style=""><br></p></section></section></section><section><section><section><section><br></section></section></section></section><section><section><section><section><strong>5</strong></section></section></section></section><section><section><section><section><br></section><p style="text-align: center;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" src="https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/E98H7dujLV5ozib26aXThep73b8EcYGNiauiaBfUbJTNplvibWYGhpSfIlPSdtQiaD4ibnWvdcHmuEzb2fYIx6a9jWUg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="1.70863309352518" data-w="" class="fr-dii" style="width: 360px;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br></p><section><section><section><section><section><strong>6</strong></section></section></section></section><section><section><section><section>&ldquo;你中午想吃啥呀&rdquo;<br></section><section>&ldquo;红枣茶和炸鸡排吧！&rdquo;</section><section>&ldquo;把排字去了！&rdquo;</section><p style="text-align: center;">&ldquo;......&rdquo;</p><p style="text-align: center;"><br></p></section></section></section><section><section><section><p style="text-align: center;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" src="https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/E98H7dujLV5ozib26aXThep73b8EcYGNiaZTl40m207C4pOKN8zmFyp4oyBkAhiaAX1A9jysNykhPbkdKomICXpZg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="1.0629496402877698" data-w="" class="fr-dii" style="width: 378px;"><br></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br></p></section></section></section><section><section>