ei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 2em; text-align: center; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">最真实的声音</span></span></strong></span></p><p><br></p><p><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><img class="fr-dib" src="http://www.campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/5714ea9b377e8.gif" style="width: 300px;"></span></span></strong></span><br></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">本期人物：<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">任迅池</span></span></span></span></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">西华大学</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">2013</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">级学生</span></span></span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">建筑与土木学院 &nbsp;城乡规划专业</span></span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">第八届66轮滑社社长</span></span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">西区轮滑赛新生赛团体第一</span></span></span></span></p><div><br></div><hr><p><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">在成为轮滑社社长的那一刻，任<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">迅</span></strong>池感到了惊喜的荣幸，似乎又有种成为大神的幸福感。</span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">因为在体育类的社团里，最重要的就是以技术服人，&ldquo;能做这个社长，是大家对我的肯定，我也只是想把大家带好，让社团更好的发展下去。&rdquo;</span></span></p><p style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;">与轮滑结缘，那是很早之前了。他在小学三年级就有过接触。那时主要是通过自己找视频模仿练习，并没有让什么人很专业的去教，就是靠兴趣苦练。<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">小小的人，小小的脚，小小的轮滑鞋。关于轮滑的小小梦想随着轮子一起飞驰着。</strong></span></p><p><br></p><p><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img class="fr-dib" src="http://www.campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/5714eb216e83e.jpeg" style="width: 724px;"></strong></span><br></p><p style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;">而真正系统的学习是在大学后才开始的。任<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">迅</span>池主要练的是平花，刹车也会一些，他笑说&ldquo;可能是出于舍不得轮子的心情吧&rdquo;。在大二下学期时，因为滑得太快控制不及时受了严重的伤，在腿上留下了很大一块疤。我问他有没有以后始终往轮滑方向发展，他给出了这样的回答：&ldquo;<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">其实我觉得我觉得如果是第一的兴趣爱好最好作为纯玩，第二的可以作为职业，因为我不想让职业使我的兴趣被破坏</strong>，有时工作是件无聊的事，就像游戏职业玩家不再能体会到游戏的乐趣吧。轮滑俱乐部虽然好，但是到了现在我还是要更多的考虑现实，成本上确实是很大的，所以我还是要从基础做起。&rdquo;</span></p><p style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;">成长的过程，也就是务实的过程吧。到了大三，任<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">迅</span>池少了很多梦幻的东西，更多想的是就业。<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">他喜欢自由，但是还要有稳定的生活才能去追求，专业课可以让他学到很多</strong>，包括设计类他也觉得可以去发展，当然，轮滑也是他的选择之一。</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><img class="fr-dib" src="http://www.campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/5714eb625f387.jpeg" style="width: 544px;"></span><br></p><p><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">学生时代最让我们珍视的，或许就是那些纯粹的无关利益的感情了吧。在社团生活</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">这几年，他收获了很多朋友，结识了志同道合的人。在这些朋友间没有很多的世俗，也没有那些制度和级别，只是大家一起开心的玩，用技术说话，他可以完全放松地和大家敞开心扉。</span></span></span></p><div><p style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">靠兴趣和团队的责任心与感觉来凝聚社团是他的理念。66的等级感并不像学生会之类的那么分明，大家因为兴趣而来，因为情感而停留，比起学生会的利益勾连，大家想要的是自己的技术被其他人肯定。任迅池谈到，66的人员流动性很高，很多人只是一时兴起又很快为了自己的各种原因而放弃，他希望大家能多坚持下去。</span></span></p></div><p><br></p><p><img class="fr-dib" src="http://www.campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/5714eba670090.gif" style="width: 300px;"><img class="fr-dib" src="http://www.campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/5714ebc015a6c.gif" style="width: 300px;"></p><p><br></p><p><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;">经营一个社团，许多时候也需要考虑现实层面的问题。社团资金方面，需要的并不多，装备都是大家自己买的，活动比赛一般用我们的内部资金。&ldquo;66自己举办的活动不是很多，主要是外出的交流联系，但是平时的一些活动啦，表演啦，还是很多的，不需要太多的限制，一个场地，约个时间，随时都可以。&rdquo;社团的兴趣属性让一切都显得更自由宽松，也使得大家的相处更加融洽。</span></p><p><br></p><p><img class="fr-dib" src="http://www.campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/5714ec2594302.jpeg" style="width: 723px;"></p><p style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></p><p style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">一个丰富的人，生活也会在横向衍生出许多个自己。<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">任迅池很喜欢摄影，帮忙拍过一些宣传片，还给自己做了些明信片来装饰房间，毕业季的时候也会去帮朋友们拍毕业照。</strong>他曾经去过西安学习手绘。他的眼中，自己算是个吃货，游山玩水吃遍各地的美食。目前他还在市里几家轮滑俱乐部做做兼职教练，也是爱好带给他的新体验吧。</span></span></p><p style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">生活给了我们无数次机会去冒险，去尝试，年轻就是要努力给自己多一些可能。我仿佛看到了，他能穿着这双轮滑鞋，不断地飞向新的宇宙。</span></span></strong></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img class="fr-dib" src="http://www.campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/5714eca88b3eb.gif" style="width: 300px;"><br></p><p><br></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;">原文详见campusleader微信公共号</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><a href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzAwNTg2MjA2MQ==&mid=2671615690&idx=1&sn=cf15ebf16ed9e66e1355c209fb8f601c&scene=0#wechat_redirect">链接：壹七专访 | 任迅池，轮滑少年飞翔手记</a><embed id="xunlei_com_thunder_helper_plugin_d462f475-c18e-46be-bd10-327458d045bd" type="application/thunder_download_plugin" height="0" width="0"></span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><embed id="xunlei_com_thunder_helper_plugin_d462f475-c18e-46be-bd10-327458d045bd" type="application/thunder_download_plugin" height="0" width="0"><embed id="xunlei_com_thunder_helper_plugin_d462f475-c18e-46be-bd10-327458d045bd" type="application/thunder_download_plugin" height="0" width="0">', '2016-04-18 22:21:52', 128, '22', 4, 4, 0, '5714ed8033dac.jpeg', '5714ed8033dac_thumb.jpeg'),
(122, '南航大学生发起戴眼罩亲吻陌生人活动', '别人家的大学生都亲上啦！', '<p><span style="font-size: 18px;">近日，《在大学里和陌生人kiss，原来是这样的一种体验》在南京航空航天大学朋友圈热传。创作者柳可是南航在读本科生，他在南京高校发起&ldquo;你好，陌生人&rdquo;活动，邀请南京高校20名大学生，来到南航参与&ldquo;戏剧性的相遇&rdquo;&mdash;&mdash;戴上眼罩，在没有见过对方的情况下，用亲吻的方式来交流感情。</span></p><p><br></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px;"><img class="fr-dib" src="http://campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/57039d3a14473.jpg" style="width: 300px;"></span><span style="font-family: ''Myriad Set Pro'', ''Hiragino Sans GB W3'', å¾®è½¯é›…é»‘â€˜, YaHei, ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Lucida Grande'', ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif, SHSCN, ''Open Sans''; font-size: 18px;">会玩的</span></p><p><br></p><p><img class="fr-dib" src="http://campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/57039d4878a35.jpg" style="width: 300px;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: ''Myriad Set Pro'', ''Hiragino Sans GB W3'', å¾®è½¯é›…é»‘â€˜, YaHei, ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Lucida Grande'', ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif, SHSCN, ''Open Sans''; text-align: center; font-size: 18px;">妹子害羞了</span></p><p><br></p><p><img class="fr-dib" src="http://campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/57039d58856c3.jpg" style="width: 300px;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: ''Myriad Set Pro'', ''Hiragino Sans GB W3'', å¾®è½¯é›…é»‘â€˜, YaHei, ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Lucida Grande'', ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif, SHSCN, ''Open Sans''; text-align: center; font-size: 18px;">这？！竟然是两个汉子</span></p><p><br></p><p><img class="fr-dib" src="http://campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/57039d81cd5af.jpg" style="width: 300px;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: ''Myriad Set Pro'', ''Hiragino Sans GB W3'', å¾®è½¯é›…é»‘â€˜, YaHei, ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Lucida Grande'', ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif, SHSCN, ''Open Sans''; text-align: center; font-size: 18px;">不过他们似乎很享受的样子，嘿嘿</span></p><p><br></p><p><img class="fr-dib" src="http://campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/57039f537089a.jpg" style="width: 300px;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">汉子好主动</span></p><p><br></p><p><img class="fr-dib" src="http://campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/57039f6348bab.jpg" style="width: 300px;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">干嘛不在一起！</span></p><p><br></p><p><img class="fr-dib" src="http://campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/57039f75bc8ee.jpg" style="width: 300px;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">你想像图片上的同学那样也来一次陌生人之间的kiss吗？</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">反正小编挺想的，哈哈</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br></p><p style="text-align: center;">campus leader</p><p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;编辑：小明</p>', '2016-04-05 19:43:55', 588, '8', 8, 29, 0, '5703a4fb27782.jpg', '5703a4fb27782_thumb.jpg');
