 break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;">只是在走进</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 2em; text-align: center; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;">一个温暖而可爱的人</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 2em; text-align: center; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;">我们</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 2em; text-align: center; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;">只是想听见</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 2em; text-align: center; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;">最真实的声音</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 34.1333px; text-align: center; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;</p><p><img class="fr-dib" src="http://www.campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/570e640a1e919.jpeg" style="width: 643px;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">本期人物：王然</strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">Itea house众创空间创始人</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">杭州沐木企业管理咨询有限公司创始人</p><p><br></p><hr><p><embed id="xunlei_com_thunder_helper_plugin_d462f475-c18e-46be-bd10-327458d045bd" type="application/thunder_download_plugin" height="0" width="0"></p><p><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;">创业两个字轻飘飘的，可只有经历过的人才会懂得，这条千难万险的创业路上每个沉甸甸的脚印。</span>15<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;">年</span>4<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;">月，杭州的创业风潮开始由点及面地扩散。我们喊着&ldquo;大众创新，万众创业&rdquo;的口号投身于各种形式的创业里。与此同时，创业服务也作为一个衍生产业在迅速发展。</span></span></p><p><br></p><p><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;">王然就是一个投身于创业服务的年轻人。采访那夜，我匆忙赶至</span>Itea house<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;">众创空间。也是在那个众多想法的起航站里，我开始一点点去了解关于这个年轻创业者一路走来的心路历程。</span></span></p><p><br></p><p><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;"><img class="fr-dib" src="http://www.campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/570e653f8d1a1.jpeg" style="width: 626px;"></span></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: normal; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;"><img class="fr-dib" src="http://www.campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/570e65c34be0d.jpeg" style="width: 622px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">itea house众创空间内景</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;">初见他时他仍在办公室忙碌，像个不会累的发条人。我很讶异于他惊人的战斗力，笑问他有没有觉得自己患上了工作症。他倒是显得不以为然，&ldquo;基本上工作时间嘛，十几个小时吧，可以说没有生活。我就这么坦白，讲没有生活的。因为我们也没有完整的，比如说没有周末的，就每天基本上都一样的。大多数创业者应该差不多都是这样，因为我见到的所有的创业者，比如创始人或者合伙人，大多数我都没有见过他们按时按点下班的。&rdquo;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: normal; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: normal; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;">忙碌好像已经成为了所有创业者的标签，因为空闲对他们而言就意味着项目的暂缓、停滞。一旦停下来，对业务不足的担忧反而会变成巨大的恐慌，逼得人抓狂。&ldquo;作为一家公司的创始人也好，还是合伙人也好，其实都想着这家公司越来越好，你想他越来越好的时候肯定是越忙才会越来越好，因为你越来越空的时候证明这家公司其实可能在走下坡路了。&rdquo;</span></p><p><br></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="fr-dib" src="http://www.campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/570e6637efb5a.jpeg" style="width: 391px;"><br></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;">一个像发条人一样的王然，就好像天注定他将成为一个创业者。他的创业之路在高中时期就可窥到一丝冥冥的迹象。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;">&ldquo;因为我们也在做创业服务这块东西，然后从我们的观察来讲<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">大多数创业者受影响力最大应该是来自于家庭</strong>。说实话我的家庭是不太好啦，我们最早的时候是在高二的时候，在我们学校那个教学楼。那时候我们还有卖零食的，我那时候就去卖零食，跟现在这种寝室楼卖零食的方式是应该差不多的。我们那时候可能跟现在（相比）就是没有互联网下单。我们一般教室里面有五十多号人，很多人可能就是说早饭不吃，我们就把这些零食放在自己的桌子里面，他们就来买。这样，这是最原始的。高三的时候好像那时候还去做过小生意这些，就是倒卖过那种学英语用的记忆卡片，我就卖过那个东西。&rdquo;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: normal; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: normal; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;">高中时的小贩生活使他产生了对于&ldquo;做生意&rdquo;的模糊概念。但大一大二他却并没有立马就开始创业，相反，他甚至完全与创业没有交集。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: normal; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: normal; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;">&ldquo;</span><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;">我觉得在自己没有机会的时候，就不断的为了那个机会去积累自己的能力。</span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;">所以我大一大二的时候基本上是在学校团委工作：先是担任校青年志愿者协会副会长，后来大二担任校团委宣传部部长。这两年让我养成了良好的工作习惯，这或许是在课本上收获不了的。别人可能就大一大二一直在折腾哦，在做些小生意之类的，我接触的这种人也有的，一直在做，不停在折腾，不停在做一些校园生意之类的，我没有。<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">我觉得做一件事还是纯粹点好</strong>，别在你最宝贵的大学生活里，献给那些追求利益的小生意，培养能力才是关键。</span></span></p><p><br></p><p><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;"><img class="fr-dib" src="http://www.campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/570e666db930d.jpeg" style="width: 607px;"></span></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">我觉得那两年最大的感受可能是处事方式和工作方法。</strong>它给后来的创业其实还奠定了很多的东西。因为我觉得在部门里面工作以后，有老师，有部员，而部员就像你现在的员工一样，你要去想很多事情，然后学校里面有活动或工作上的限制就像在社会上各类规章制度和条例一样。我觉得学生工作让你在大学里面还是收获了蛮多东西的，这可能是在其他学习上或者说去做兼职都得不到的东西。然后我们看到下沙有很多创业者基本上都是学生会主席、副主席出身的。说到这个，马云以前也是学生会主席嘞，真的！杭师大，他是那时候杭师大学生会副主席，我觉得学生工作还是真的蛮有帮助的，我是这么认为的。&rdquo;</span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: normal; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;">韬光养晦四字是很含哲学意味的，对于人生而言，某个阶段的沉默可能会比时时刻刻的进取来得更有意义。厚积薄发、量变产生质变，大约都是这个理儿。他说他其实并不认同校园领袖这种说法，因为毕业之后产生的变数是我们无法预计的，&ldquo;大学是你人生重要一站，不是尽头。大学是你人生重要的一个起点，你能跟别人讲在起点的时候你是个领袖吗？我觉得没有领袖这一说的，只能说在某个特定的领域、特定的环境里面这个人相对来讲是比较优秀的。&rdquo;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;">他有种谦恭的气质，与先前我想的生意人相距甚远。我在他身上，闻不到传统商人的铜臭味。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;">谦谦君子，用涉大川。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;">一个对周遭世界心怀敬意的人，大抵就是如此吧。</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>他的故事，还没说完</strong></span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>在他创业期间又发生了什么呢？</strong></span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>壹七专访</strong></span></span></span></p><div style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center; white-space: pre-wrap; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>下期继续为您讲述</strong></span></span></div><div style="text-align: center;"><strong>更多后续报道，</strong><strong>详见</strong></div><div style="text-align: center;"><span style="line-height: 1.8; font-family: ''Myriad Set Pro'', ''Hiragino Sans GB W3'', å¾®è½¯é›…é»‘â€˜, YaHei, ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Lucida Grande'', ''Helvetica Neue'', H