10px; border-left-width: 10px; border-left-color: rgba(249, 221, 31, 0.992157); border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; box-shadow: rgb(153, 153, 153) 2px 2px 4px; text-shadow: rgb(34, 95, 135) 0px 1px 0px; background-color: rgb(55, 57, 57); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Q9：创业应该是很忙的吧，那在创业之余，你有没有什么其他的兴趣爱好来陶冶自己的情操呢？</span></span></span></strong></span></strong></span></blockquote></section><p></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></span></span><br></p><p style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">A9：目前有两大爱好：读书、唱歌。我很喜欢读书，历史、社会、心理、哲学、经济、管理、小说等等，尤其对侦探小说很痴迷。也很喜欢路遥、贾平凹等西北的作家。我在家里的藏书有好几百本。至于唱歌，我比较喜欢陕北民<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">歌，也痴迷民谣、相声、秦腔等。</span></span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">另外有一个正在养成的爱好是学习乐器，我想学习古琴。我性子比较急，创业压力也会比较大，古琴可以让我舒缓身心，会带给我不一样的体验。</span></span></span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 18px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">关于他的故事</span></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 18px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">原文详见campusleader微信公共号</span></span></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 18px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><a href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzAwNTg2MjA2MQ==&mid=2671615784&idx=1&sn=c2a5556f7ca5f704dfffe0effb83da17&scene=0#wechat_redirect">链接：壹七专访 | 石老大，我在江湖你在哪</a><embed id="xunlei_com_thunder_helper_plugin_d462f475-c18e-46be-bd10-327458d045bd" type="application/thunder_download_plugin" height="0" width="0"></span><br></span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></span></span><br></p><p><embed id="xunlei_com_thunder_helper_plugin_d462f475-c18e-46be-bd10-327458d045bd" type="application/thunder_download_plugin" height="0" width="0"></p><embed id="xunlei_com_thunder_helper_plugin_d462f475-c18e-46be-bd10-327458d045bd" type="application/thunder_download_plugin" height="0" width="0"><embed id="xunlei_com_thunder_helper_plugin_d462f475-c18e-46be-bd10-327458d045bd" type="application/thunder_download_plugin" height="0" width="0">', '2016-04-27 18:42:39', 120, '22', 4, 4, 0, '5720979f4ba2b.jpg', '5720979f4ba2b_thumb.jpg');
