ortant; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><blockquote class="" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 5px 15px; border: 0px currentcolor; border-top-left-radius: 5px; border-top-right-radius: 5px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25px; font-weight: bold; display: inline-block; background-color: rgb(193, 193, 193); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">获奖</span></span></span></blockquote><blockquote class="" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 15px; border-width: 1px; border-top-style: solid; border-right-style: solid; border-bottom-style: solid; border-color: rgb(193, 193, 193); line-height: 25px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 25.6px;">中国计量大学新媒体工作优秀个人</span><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">中国计量大学优团</span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">中国计量大学优干</span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">浙江省优秀团员候选人</span></span></span></p></blockquote></section><p></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></span><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">在高考各种阴差阳错之下，梁天琪来到了中国计量大学，学习能源工科。为了向我解释他的专业，他笑说他是个烧锅炉专业户。抱着既来之则安之的心态，他在计量开始了他的大学小日子。</span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">其实，他和社联的缘分并没有我想象中的一帆风顺。刚开始进大学的时候，新人梁天琪只加了院学生会和一个粤语社团。到了第二学期，一次路过，他凑巧碰上了社团联的招新。而隔壁班的班长恰巧正是社联成员，在他的&ldquo;怂恿&rdquo;下，梁天琪递上了自己的报名表。于是，在完全不知道自己加了什么部门的情况下，他一头雾水地和未来3年的幸福撞个满怀。</span></span></p><p><br></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center; white-space: pre-wrap; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 30px;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">他的故事<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">你，在听吗</span></span></span></strong></p><p><br></p><p><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><br></span></span><br></p><p></p><section class="" data-source="bj.96weixin.com" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><blockquote class="" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px; border-left-width: 10px; border-left-color: rgba(249, 221, 31, 0.992157); border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; box-shadow: rgb(153, 153, 153) 2px 2px 4px; text-shadow: rgb(34, 95, 135) 0px 1px 0px; background-color: rgb(55, 57, 57); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">Q1<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">:</span></strong></span></strong></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">你觉得校级社团和院级社团最大的区别在于哪里？</span></span></span></span></blockquote></section><p></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em;">院会的优点是你认识的人都紧紧是院里面的同学，以后不管是你做班级事情也好，还是说做项目做科研，以及做班级联欢，都有好多好多熟人，你做事情也很方便。但是你在校级组织里面你会认识更多的其他平台的人，就如果我们这一批走出去的人他会担任其他学校的，比如说其他学院的院会的主席团或者说比如说现在我们学校党委宣传部的微博协会会长也是我们以前同级的干事，加上还有一些比如说</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em;">航模队</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em;">的队长等等都是我在校级组织历练认识下的人。</span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">比起社会上，大学里更多的是一个交集，我觉得加学生组织你不可能说你真的是为了学到更多东西，我的目的是仅仅说是交到更多的朋友，不仅仅是窝在宿舍里，大门不出二门不迈的打打游戏学学习，那不是现在当代大学生应该活的。而且为了，党中央、团中央的三走嘛，走下网络，走出寝室，走向操场，那我平时也会去健身跑步，这边还有一个社联工作，然后考研的时候会备战去考研，我觉得这是生活，应该有的一个健康的状态，那不至于就觉得太无聊，是这样一个。</span></span></p><p><br></p><p><img class="fr-dib" src="http://www.campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/573c795de1937.jpeg" style="width: 616px;"><br></p><p><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><br></span></span><br></p><p></p><section class="" data-source="bj.96weixin.com" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><blockquote class="" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px; border-left-width: 10px; border-left-color: rgba(249, 221, 31, 0.992157); border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; box-shadow: rgb(153, 153, 153) 2px 2px 4px; text-shadow: rgb(34, 95, 135) 0px 1px 0px; background-color: rgb(55, 57, 57); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">Q2:</span></span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">最开始你对社联是什么感觉？</span></span></span></span></span></blockquote></section><p></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em;">我，嗯，因为是下学期进的社联，然后第一次聚餐的时候部长给我发消息说哪里哪里聚餐，我找了个借口拒绝掉了，我说我跟一个朋友要看电影那天，说是我喜欢的女生，要跟她去看电影，然后他说行行行，就放我去了，其实我根本没有事情做。因为我是觉得那个时间段我融不进这个集体，我觉得这个集体对我而言没有一种吸引力，没有像院会那种更亲近。</span><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></span><br></p><p></p><section class="" data-source="bj.96weixin.com" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><blockquote class="" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px; border-left-width: 10px; border-left-color: rgba(249, 221, 31, 0.992157); border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; box-shadow: rgb(153, 153, 153) 2px 2px 4px; text-shadow: rgb(34, 95, 135) 0px 1px 0px; background-color: rgb(55, 57, 57); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">Q3：</span></strong></span></strong></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">那是哪一个瞬间让你觉得突然间融入进去了？</span></span></span></blockquote></section><p></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em;">这个瞬间我真的很清楚，大概在大一的时候我们那次接了一个某饮料的赞助，主要任务是给大家分发饮料。但是那个饮料呢，赞助商那边需要回收饮料瓶的瓶盖，就是说，我们给同学的只能是一瓶拿开盖子的饮料，盖子我们需要拿掉。所以我过去一直拧瓶盖拧瓶盖，一直到下午三点多，那样饮料差不多大概有一千多瓶。然后我拧拧拧，拧到了手里皮都破了，都流血了。我的副部长就立马去给我买了那个创可贴给我贴上，还把其他所有容易受伤的部分都贴上了，再拧起来就比较舒服。</span><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">我突然就觉得那个副部长真的好像我一个姐姐，就可能感受到了你的部长对你的亲切和很真诚的关怀，这是在我院会里可能只是没机会体会到的，如果有这个机会，我相信我院会的部长也会对我这样子，只是我在这里呢，真真切切的体会到了那种家文化的感觉，所以我是从那个瞬间开始我是特别想要留在这里。</span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></span><br></p><p></p><section class="" data-source="bj.96weixin.com" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><blockquote class="" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px; border-left-width: 10px; border-left-color: rgba(249, 221, 31, 0.992157); border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; box-shadow: rgb(153, 153, 153) 2px 2px 4px; text-shadow: rgb(34, 95, 135) 0px 1px 0px; background-color: rgb(55, 57, 57); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 0em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;"><span style