><span style="font-size: 16px;">那凝聚组织的话首先，那肯定是说你要有一定的领导力。我对这个方面的概念也不是很清楚，但我觉得最重要的是一个亲和力吧，如果你作为一个部长，你仅仅是对你下面的手下干事命令式的语气，开会一本正经的话，然后平时的接触也仅仅局限在你事务上的一些关联。干事会觉得你这个人，太高了，或者说遥不可及，就你完全没法触及到你部长私下里的生活，没法跟他做朋友。</span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">说老实话，大学里，你也不拿工资，你作为组织的话又不是说真的是上下级的关系，你更多的是一个朋友的关系。还有就是学长对学弟或者学妹的一种关怀，生活里关怀，私下里关怀，感情上的关怀，都可以。</span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">当然，如果你的部长仅仅是一个开会时一点严肃感都没有，就嘻嘻哈哈，闹腾闹腾，那大家可能就会打闹在一起，但是一旦真的要做起事情来说你给人家下了一个命令，人家会觉得你是开玩笑，拖两天也没事，或者不去也没事，那你的部门比如说半个活动的话到场率会很低，所以就需要一个两者结合。我会上会有高冷的一个态度跟他们讲事情，私下里就是会很闹腾，这肯定是需要一个两面性吧。</span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></span><br></p><p></p><section class="" data-source="bj.96weixin.com" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><blockquote class="" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; 