 word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><br></span></span><br></p><p></p><section class="" data-source="bj.96weixin.com" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><blockquote class="" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px; border-left-width: 10px; border-left-color: rgba(249, 221, 31, 0.992157); border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; box-shadow: rgb(153, 153, 153) 2px 2px 4px; text-shadow: rgb(34, 95, 135) 0px 1px 0px; background-color: rgb(55, 57, 57); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 0em;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">Q7</span></strong></span><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">：</span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">很多学生组织总会面临社员退部的问题，你觉得有哪些原因呢？</span></span></span></span></span></p></blockquote></section><p></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">我以前的部门退部率也是蛮高的，好多人就是过了一个学期就退掉了。我后面总结出来，主要是因为好多干事他对部门的融入感不强。社联他一直倡导的是一个家文化，就把自己的组织当作自己的家一样去看待，大家都是兄弟姐妹，但是好多退部的干事他退部的真正原因是因为他感觉自己没法融进去。我以前做干事的时候我也碰到过这种问题。</span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">特别是开会的时候特别长，五米长的桌子，一般坐在这里的干事和坐在这里的靠近你的干事是比较活跃的，如果是坐在这个以后这样，坐在后面的干事，他是可能有一种对自我的保护，他不想就是部长问到你问题你答不上来的一种羞愧感吧。然后还有一个是，他对这个部门不够热爱，他已经感受不到当初进这个部门时的一腔热血，他过一段时间就会退。</span></span></p><p><br></p><p><img class="fr-dib" src="http://www.campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/573c7dd3d95ef.jpeg" style="width: 449px;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><br></span></span></span></p><p><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">很多团队领导者会大谈情怀、梦想，用空洞却不实在的幻象去满足队员的白日梦心理。但空终究为空，不实在的棉花团是无法抵挡风雨的。人心齐，则事半功倍。当一个团队纯粹由情感凝聚时，那份团结才是沉甸甸的，才会有真正的力量感。</span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">梁天琪是聪明的，但我更想说他是真挚的。能让他带领团队走到现在的，绝不是方法本身，而是他对待每个人的赤子之心。</span></span></span></p><p><br></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 18px;"><strong>关于他的故事，</strong><span style="color: rgb(17, 17, 17);"><strong>原文详见campusleader微信公众号</strong></span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><a href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzAwNTg2MjA2MQ==&mid=524132300&idx=1&sn=770b05b321d3f595cbca84ec0f819537#rd"><strong><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">链接：壹七专访 | 梁天琪，我的社联我的家</span></span></strong></a><embed id="xunlei_com_thunder_helper_plugin_d462f475-c18e-46be-bd10-327458d045bd" type="application/thunder_download_plugin" height="0" width="0"><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></p><p><embed id="xunlei_com_thunder_helper_plugin_d462f475-c18e-46be-bd10-327458d045bd" type="application/thunder_download_plugin" height="0" width="0"><embed id="xunlei_com_thunder_helper_plugin_d462f475-c18e-46be-bd10-327458d045bd" type="application/thunder_download_plugin" height="0" width="0"></p><p><embed id="xunlei_com_thunder_helper_plugin_d462f475-c18e-46be-bd10-327458d045bd" type="application/thunder_download_plugin" height="0" width="0"><embed id="xunlei_com_thunder_helper_plugin_d462f475-c18e-46be-bd10-327458d045bd" type="application/thunder_download_plugin" height="0" width="0"><embed id="xunlei_com_thunder_helper_plugin_d462f475-c18e-46be-bd10-327458d045bd" type="application/thunder_download_plugin" height="0" width="0"></p><p><embed id="xunlei_com_thunder_helper_plugin_d462f475-c18e-46be-bd10-327458d045bd" type="application/thunder_download_plugin" height="0" width="0"><embed id="xunlei_com_thunder_helper_plugin_d462f475-c18e-46be-bd10-327458d045bd" type="application/thunder_download_plugin" height="0" width="0"></p><embed id="xunlei_c