: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">Q9：</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; text-indent: 37px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">我们现在看到的产品其实是个组团协作平台，也就是说最初的想法到现在有了一些调整是么？</span></span></span></span></p></blockquote></section><p></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">是有很大的调整。因为我发现创业这个切口其实太窄了些，没办法很深刻地去切入大学生的成长，因为很多人其实只是想就业。但我觉得大学生创业其实更多的是一种实践，因为我们都知道高校创业万死万生。大学生创业背后真正的金矿不在项目在人，失败的创业可以转化为成功的就业，不仅仅是leader，也包括所有的参与者，因为这个过程让能让所有的参与者获得成长，也会留下真实的痕迹。我的产品正在朝着这样的方向调整，让大家能够在这里成全彼此。</span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6