ortant; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">好像我们都经历过这种时刻，明明拿着手机大骂&ldquo;你</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">是在逗我吗&rdquo;，但发过去的却是</span></span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; border: none; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&ldquo;嗯嗯，好的！&rdquo;</span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; border: none; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&ldquo;没关系，我再给你解释一下！&rdquo;</span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; border: none; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">&ldquo;辛苦啦</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">~</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">么么哒！&rdquo;</span></span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; border: none; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&hellip;&hellip;</span></span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; border: none; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">而往往，越是&ldquo;身居高位&rdquo;，越是不得不去照顾这些人际关系。<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">从小到大习惯了领导身份的陆晨曦，对此显然并不陌生。</span></strong></span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; border: none; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; border: none; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">&ldquo;你在这个位置上，别人有求于你的时候，你回复他，你给他帮助是你在这个位置上应该做的事情，那我觉得你要把自己的职责去做好，你不能因为这个人傻</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">b</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">吧，你就不理他，那这个错就在你了，对吧，<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">所以就做好你自己吧，该做什么做什么呗</span></strong>，就不管怎么样，你要做学生干部就是经常有时候别人啪一个微信发过来。你一看，就忍不住骂（凶狠脸）：你这都看不懂吗？！#￥&amp;*%&hellip;&hellip;@ &nbsp; 然后狂骂一通之后，却回复（乖巧脸）：嗯好~你这个地方呢，其实是这个样子的balabalabala&hellip;&hellip;不懂得可以再问我哦！&rdquo;</span></span></span></span></p><p><br></p><p><img class="fr-dib" src="http://www.campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/5746f87442585.jpeg" style="width: 376px;"></p><p><br></p><p><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&ldquo;不管你是在学校的各大组织里面还是在班级里面，那都是这样子的，因为你在这个位置，特别是我现在到了副团这个位置，有时候别人可能会认为你代表着艺术团，甚至你代表着浙江传媒学院，那没有办法，你就是永远得好好跟人家说话。&rdquo;</span></span></span></p><p><br></p><p><img class="fr-dib" src="http://www.campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/5746f8b9c551d.jpeg" style="width: 642px;"><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; border: none; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">&ldquo;我的职位的大体就是老师给你一个统筹的观念，那接下来就是我去执行的问题，所以老师一般很少会再去跟下面的人具体的说你要如何如何之类的，而且我们从大一进来开始，基本上各个部长也会告诉你。<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">其实艺术团就是一个以做晚会做这种东西为核心的一个地方</span></strong>，对吧。那你肯定要知道在活动现场要以活动为重，我从大一进来，从面试艺术团开始就是这个观念灌输给我们，一定要以活动现场为重，那可能你会受委屈啊等等，我们可以私下去解决，去干嘛，去吐槽，都可以</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">。<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">但是在那个场面上不可以耽误，因为大家都知道现场一分一秒都很重要。</span></strong>&rdquo;</span></span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></span></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></p><p></p><section class="" data-source="bj.96weixin.com" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0.8em 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; line-height: 25px; font-family: 微软雅黑; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span class="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0.3em 0.5em; border-top-left-radius: 0.5em; border-top-right-radius: 0.5em; border-bottom-right-radius: 0.5em; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.5em; text-align: center; color: white; display: inline-block; box-shadow: rgb(165, 165, 165) 0.2em 0.2em 0.1em; background-color: rgb(247, 228, 17); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">笑 &middot; 传媒理想还是要有的</span></span></span></strong></span></section></section><p></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></span></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(120, 172, 254);"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&ldquo;上辈子不学好、这辈子干编导。上辈子做坏人，这辈子电视人。&rdquo;</span></span></span></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">虽然这种调侃的语言在传媒学院随处可闻，可是每个传媒学子依旧享受着台前幕后的所有时光。</span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&ldquo;以我的性格好像更喜欢待在台前，包括我自己学的播音主持，但是我觉得在艺术团，<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">它让我看到了在幕后的这种有意思的地方，特别是我大一的时候参加了很多晚会吧，我觉得幕后挺有意思的</span></strong>。因为我高中所有的，我从进校到我毕业，所有的晚会、比赛，基本上都是我在主持，所以就已经，就觉得台前也就这么回事儿吧，那可能台后对我来说更加神秘，而且我们学校的晚会比较上档次，所以就觉得会比在台前有意思，因为台前自己就是这个专业的，也就还好。&rdquo;</span></span></span></p><p><br></p><p><img class="fr-dib" src="http://www.campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/5746f90579a85.jpeg" style="width: 576px;"><br></p><p><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">&ldquo;其实对我来说每次完成一个都很开心啊，那你要说最难忘，那肯定是我自己第一次当执行导演，就十佳那次，我还记得那天我，我们是在桐乡办的，回来也挺晚的了，九点多才上的车还是怎么的，然后回来的那个校车上然后其实我挺感慨的，因为我自己做的第一场大型活动吧，就是<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">有很多地方我们都不熟悉啊之类的，但是也还是成功的办下来了</span></strong>。还有一次我不记得是什么时候了，反正也是团里的一次活动也在桐乡，我回来，回来已经十一点多了，然后，啊应该是迎新晚会吧，不对啊，那天特别特别冷，然后我回来十一点多，风特别大，经过国交的时候就有一种我要死在这儿了，寸步难行。当时觉得办活动特别辛苦啊什么的，<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">但是我觉得成就感比辛苦更有意义吧</span></strong>&rdquo;</span></span></span></span></p><p><br></p><p><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img class="fr-dib" src="http://www.campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/5746f94953ed1.jpeg" style="width: 567px;"></span></span></span></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; border: none; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">晨曦姐说她真的<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">很爱主持</span></strong>，这是一件她想要努力做好的事情。我不知道这种执着算不算梦想，但是她和我讲那些故事的时候，我的眼睛热热的。</span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; border: none; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></span></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; border: none; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&ldquo;就是我第一次跟台里出去拍节目的时候，编导说，行，这个镜头你出一下，你就说个开场白就行，完全是懵的，不知道说什么，然后编导就跟我说，哦，那你看看周围环境怎么样啊，你要怎么怎么说啊，然后给了我几个关键句，然后自己拼凑了一下，<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">那到现在，我基本上就是，到了点，他把镜头架好的过程，他把脚架架好的过程中我就想好我要说什么了</span></strong>，然后一般录个两三条就可以过了。我第一次去拍节目，去录，因为我们是一个旅游节目，一个镜头大概录了，就一段口播我大概录了七八遍吧，就很尴尬就很尴尬，真的是老师有这个容忍度，就是觉得你是个学生，他也没有点破说你看吧，你们学院派不行吧这种，可是自己就觉得很尴尬。然后你会知道自己学校里学的跟外面的还差很多，嗯。&rdquo;</span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; border: none; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; border: none; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></span></span><br></p><p></p><section class="" data-source="bj.96weixin.com" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0.8em 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; line-height: 25px; font-family: 微软雅黑; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span class="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0.3em 0.5em; border-top-left-radius: 0.5em; border-top-right-radius: 0.5em; border-bottom-right-radius: 0.5em; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.5em; text-align: center; color: white; display: inline-block; box-shadow: rgb(165, 165, 165) 0.2em 0.2em 0.1em; background-color: rgb(247, 228, 17); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">真 &middot; 要有最成熟的善良</span></span></span></strong></span></section></section><p></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></span></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; border: none; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&ldquo;我就觉得这句话莫名的很有道理，对，因为我这个人也是有时候，虽然我经常觉得自己很成熟老道啊，可是有时候也会，为什么要相信那个人，就是也会被骗啊之类的，然后包括我以前交朋友啊什么的都比较倾其所有的那种，自己在这方面比较蠢，<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">所以要有最成熟的善良，然后就慢慢慢慢的会好起来，然后慢慢慢慢的不会那么依赖人</span></strong>。&rdquo;</span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; border: none; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; border: none; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">一群人的初中，几个人的高中，一个人的大学。我们在成长中学会去接受和习惯，所有必须独自去面对的安静。</span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; border: none; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></span></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; border: none; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">&ldquo;</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">就是我可以说我是，有一点儿被这些好朋友宠成很依赖人，但是你到大学会发现就是孤独的，很多事情就是要你一个人去做去完成的，朋友不可能随时陪在你身边，我现在很多朋友出国的出国，各自在不同的城市。就是虽然我想哭的时候还是会打电话给他，就嚎啕大哭，但是我不怎么会跟大学里的朋友哭，这是真的。但是他们真的不能再帮上你什么实质性的措施，<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">然后你就会学会一个人做事情，也还好了，就一个人去图书馆也还好，一个人去健身房也还好，就习惯了就还好。</span></strong></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">&rdquo;</span></span></span></span></p><p><br></p><p><img class="fr-dib" src="http://www.campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/5746f98843449.jpeg" style="width: 642px;"></p><p><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; border: none; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">孤单，是一个人的狂欢，狂欢，是一群人的孤单。灯光落幕、观众离场之前，主持人一定会说句&ldquo;我们来年再见&rdquo;作为慰藉，可面对人潮涌退后的空荡，或许那才是最让人感慨万千的东西。</span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; border: none; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></span></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; border: none; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">&ldquo;</span><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">做完晚会之后各回各家是一件非常落寞的事情，你心里会有一丁点儿落差，就是前面乌央央所有人持续的准备了好几天，包括晚会的呈现，然后到最后全部结束了</span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">，各回各家的那种心情，我就很不喜欢那种心情，我一回家就会蒙头睡，不然就会想哭。我真的是，我会心里很难受然后就哭，哭完了也没什么就睡，然后就写东西，写完了然后一脸懵逼的就直接交，嗯，就这样吧。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">&rdquo;</span></span></span></span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">陆晨曦，她是那个吃着红豆冰的姑娘。没有我想象中无所不能、百毒不侵，却那么真实可爱。</span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">冠冕堂皇的套话像酒楼里的满汉全席，我们知道，冰凉香甜的红豆冰才最醇香四溢。</span></span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">去发掘人物本身最质朴的一面，壹七专访的意义也就在于此吧。</span></span></span></span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 18px;"><span style="font-family: ''Microsoft YaHei'';"><span style="font-size: 18px;"><strong>陆晨曦的音频彩蛋以及原文详情</strong></span></span></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 18px;"><span style="font-family: Microsoft YaHei;"><span style="font-size: 18px;"><strong><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); text-align: center;">请查看</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;">campusleader微信公众号</span></span></strong></span></span></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzAwNTg2MjA2MQ==&mid=2671616014&idx=1&sn=51b63bed440d21cffdcc31148c030d30&scene=0#wechat_redirect"><strong>链接：壹七专访 | 没想到你是这样的陆晨曦</strong></a><br></p>', '2016-05-26 21:30:28', 174, '22', 4, 4, 0, '5746fa74975cd.jpg', '5746fa74975cd_thumb.jpg');
